_Nif’al_ Imperative for regular shorushim:
The [[{{_nif’al_ imperative}} form]] follows these conjugations for [[regular shorushim]]:
|            | *Masculine* | *Feminine* |
| *Singular* | הִכָּבֵשׁ <br> _hikoveish!_ <br> [to a man] invite! | הִכָּבְשִׁי <br> _hikovshi!_ <br> [to a woman] invite! |
| *Plural*   | הִכָּבְשׁוּ <br> _hikovshu!_ <br> [to men] invite! | הִכָּבַשְׁנָה <br> _hikovashnau!_ <br> [to women] invite! |
For any regular shoresh, you can replace the letters ‎כ, ‎ב, and ש above with the letters of your shoresh to produce the proper conjugations.
